NOTE ON SYNTHETIC DATA:
The corpus data (corpus_final.csv, corpus_final.bib) contained in this repository
is SYNTHETIC and generated for methodological documentation purposes. The titles,
authors, DOIs, and venues do not represent real publications. Only the search
protocol, screening criteria, and quality assessment procedure reflect the real
SLR documented in the associated thesis.